high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the coffee table, turn right, go forward to the TV stand.
Take the center keys from the TV stand.
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go forward between the coffee table and the couch, turn right to face the couch.
Put the keys to the left of the credit card on the couch.
Turn right, go forward a step, turn right, go forward a step, turn left, go forward to the TV stand.
Take the left keys from the TV stand.
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go forward between the coffee table and the couch, turn right to face the couch.
Put the keys to the left of the first keys on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put two keys on a couch.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the coffee table, then turn right and go to the TV stand in front of you.
Pick up the set of keys between the two remotes, on the TV stand.
Turn around and go between the coffee table and the couch, then turn to the right side of the couch, on your right.
Put the keys on the couch cushion to the left of the credit card.
Turn to your right and go back to the TV stand.
Pick up the keys to the left of the remote.
Turn to your left and go back between the coffee table and the couch, then turn to the couch on your right.
Place the keys on the couch, between the two cushions.
anns.task_desc: Put two set of keys on the couch.

high_descs: Go left to face the television.
Pick the keys up from in front of the television.
Turn around and face the brown couch with a remote on it.
Put the keys on the couch.
Turn to the right and face the television stand again.
Pick the keys up from the television stand.
Turn to the left and stand in front of the brown couch again.
Put the keys down on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on a couch.
